        &lt;h2 class=&quot;section-header&quot;&gt;About the Show&lt;/h2&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Step into Monday’s Global Village, where music travels from the streets of Los Angeles to every corner of the world. Host Kathy Díaz brings a pulse of Afro Latin and Latin rhythms together with essential global sounds, unearthing voices and stories that mainstream radio leaves behind.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Every show is a celebration—lifting up local artists, shining a light on cultural traditions, and connecting neighbors across borders. In a city built on diversity, Global Village is your weekly soundtrack for community, culture, and unapologetic celebration of everything that makes us unique—right here, right now.&lt;/p&gt;
