                    &lt;h3 class=&quot;host-name&quot;&gt;Kathy Díaz&lt;/h3&gt;
                    &lt;p class=&quot;host-bio&quot;&gt;Kathy Díaz has been a passionate voice at KPFK since 1987, bringing decades of experience hosting Latin music shows across Los Angeles, Miami, and Austin. Deeply rooted in the community, Kathy is dedicated to uplifting local artists and honoring Latino culture on and off the air. As a board member for Empowering Latino Futures and an active supporter of the International Latino Book Awards, she brings both heart and history to every broadcast—always spinning real vinyl, never streaming, and always connecting community through music.&lt;/p&gt;
