Schedule and festival info at: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.arpafilmfestival.com/&quot; style=&quot;color:blue; text-decoration:underline&quot;&gt;http://www.arpafilmfestival.com/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
