&lt;b&gt;Description:&lt;/b&gt; Down on his luck in the suburbs, John Falstaff plans to hustle his way to a comfortable retirement by seducing the wives of two wealthy men. Unknown to him, it&amp;rsquo;s the women of Windsor who really pull the strings, orchestrating Falstaff&amp;rsquo;s comeuppance amidst a theatrical smorgasbord of petty rivalries, jealousies and over-inflated egos. For a fat Englishman, a Welshman and a Frenchman, the only way is Windsor&amp;hellip;Directed by Fiona Laird.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

