&lt;b&gt;Description:&lt;/b&gt; &amp;nbsp;With exclusive, unprecedented access, Westwood: Punk, Icon, Activist is the first film to encompass the remarkable story of Vivienne Westwood&amp;rsquo;s life, her fashion, her personality, her activism and her cultural importance. Since igniting the punk movement with ex-partner and Sex Pistols&amp;rsquo; manager Malcolm McLaren, Dame Vivienne Westwood has been redefining British fashion for over 40 years, and is responsible for creating many of the most distinctive looks of our time. As an activist, Vivienne Westwood has championed political causes such as the Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament, climate change and civil rights.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

