&lt;b&gt;Description:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp; Join Mystery Science Theater 3000&amp;rsquo;s &amp;ldquo;TV&amp;rsquo;s Frank&amp;rdquo; Conniff and Trace Beaulieu as they screen some of the worst movies ever made&amp;hellip;. And RIFF on them (or &amp;ldquo;comedically make fun of&amp;rdquo; them, for the MST3K-unversed)&amp;hellip;LIVE at The Frida in the same style as the Peabody Award- winning TV series! &amp;nbsp;The Mads will riff a film and a short &amp;ndash; both of which will be surprises! &amp;ndash; and will do a Q&amp;amp;A and Meet-and-Greet after the show!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
