&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Calibri&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-transform:uppercase&quot;&gt;Romeo and Juliet&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;Screens Monday August 13th (7:30 PM) and Tuesday, August 14th &amp;nbsp;(1PM) at a selected Laemmle Theater near you (Claremont 5, Playhouse 7, Royal, and Town Center 5)&lt;br /&gt;
Get more info at &amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.laemmle.com/films/44025&quot; style=&quot;color:blue; text-decoration:underline&quot;&gt;https://www.laemmle.com/films/44025&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
