Description: An Award-Winning, Action-Packed Thriller coming your way From Well Go USA!! &amp;nbsp;&amp;ldquo;&amp;hellip; an intense, fun, and entertaining thriller filled with amazing action from beginning to end&amp;rdquo;-easternKicks.com. &amp;nbsp;Director Yoon Jae-keun (Heartbeat), along with award-winning martial arts choreographers Park Young-sik and Chung Seong-Ho (SAG Awards, Best Stunt Ensemble, &amp;ldquo;Squid Game&amp;rdquo;), bring to life the action-packed thriller about a man who wakes up from a car crash, unable to remember anything about his life&amp;hellip;he begins regaining consciousness in a new body every 12 hours! &amp;nbsp;Now, he must piece together his identity, all while evading attacks from pursuing agents and dangerous criminals alike. But with no memory&amp;mdash;and no allies&amp;mdash;his time is running out. Winner of the Daniel A. Craft award for Excellence in Action Cinema at the 2021 New York Asian Film Festival, SPIRITWALKER stars former K-pop singer Yoon Kye-Sang (Chocolate, The Outlaws), Park Yong-Woo (Nailed), Lim Ji-Yeon (Obsessed, High Society) and Park Ji-Hwan (The Pirates: The Last Royal Treasure). The bonus features include an all-new English dub and behind-the-scenes content.&lt;/p&gt;

