Info and tickets here:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://arttheatre.easy-ware-ticketing.com/events?mc_cid=ffc5b1486d&amp;amp;mc_eid=677004b84b&quot;&gt;https://arttheatre.easy-ware-ticketing.com/events?mc_cid=ffc5b1486d&amp;amp;mc_eid=677004b84b&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
