Description: A two man CRIME drama starring Elijah Wood &amp;amp; Luke Kirby &amp;hellip;directed by Amber Sealey. &amp;nbsp;In 1980, Ted Bundy was sentenced to death by electrocution. &amp;nbsp;In the years that followed, he agreed to disclose the details of his crimes&amp;hellip;But only to one man. Devout Christian Bill Hagmaier is assigned by the FBI&amp;rsquo;s new profiling unit to try to get the recently convicted Ted Bundy to confess his crimes. Meeting sporadically over the course of several years, Hagmaier and Bundy build an intense and complicated bond as Hagmaier races against the clock to try to coax out a confession before Bundy is led to his state-sanctioned execution.&lt;/p&gt;

