Description: a suspense thriller from VERTICAL ENTERTAINMENT and ROADSIDE ATTRACTIONS! &amp;nbsp;Amy Carr (Naomi Watts) goes out for a restorative morning run when a friend calls her with terrifying news: the authorities are in pursuit of an active shooter, and her teenage son, Noah (Colton Gobbo), may be caught in the middle. &amp;nbsp;Deep within a network of forest paths surrounding her home, miles from town and nearly overwhelmed by panic, Amy refuses to succumb to hopelessness. &amp;nbsp;Using only her cell phone, she will draw upon every resource she can think of to ensure that her son survives the attack.&lt;/p&gt;

