SWING-- In Select Theaters October 29, VOD/Digital November 19. During their last year at an Ivy League college in 1999, a group of friends and crew teammates&amp;#39; lives are changed forever when an army vet takes over as coach of their dysfunctional rowing team. &amp;nbsp;Starring: Michael Shannon, Alexander Ludwig, Charles Melton, Alex MacNicoll, Ash Santos, Lilly Krug, David James Elliott&lt;br /&gt;
