Description: &amp;quot;This is the future generations film will be wishing everyone watched today&amp;quot;- Leonardo DiCaprio. &amp;nbsp;Academy Award-winning actress Kate Winslet narrates the astounding feature documentary Eating Our Way To Extinction taking audiences on a cinematic journey around the world. &amp;nbsp;The filmmakers tell the story of our planet through shocking testimonials, poignant accounts from indigenous people most affected by our ever-changing planet, globally renowned figures, and leading scientists. &amp;nbsp; Confronting and entertaining, this documentary allows audiences to question their everyday choices, industry leaders, and governments. World-renowned contributors include Sir Richard Branson and Tony Robbins with world-renowned scientific experts. This powerful documentary sends a simple but impactful message by uncovering hard truths and addressing the most pressing issue of our generation &amp;ndash; ecological collapse.&lt;/p&gt;

