In Select Theaters November 19, 2021&lt;br /&gt;
Get more info at the film&amp;rsquo;s Magnolia Pictures website:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.magpictures.com/badluckbanging/&quot;&gt;http://www.magpictures.com/badluckbanging/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Enjoy the trailer here:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JXG_A7ove8E&quot;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JXG_A7ove8E&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;;&amp;nbsp;Enjoy the KPFK Film Club Review here:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=3062730747335464&amp;amp;id=1718261665115719&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.facebook.com/&lt;wbr /&gt;permalink.php?story_fbid=&lt;wbr /&gt;3062730747335464&amp;amp;id=&lt;wbr /&gt;1718261665115719&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Description: Magnolia Pictures is proud to present BAD LUCK BANGING OR LOONY PORN, written and directed by Radu Jude, starring Katia Pascari. &amp;nbsp;A three-part satire that is as shocking as it is funny, Radu Jude&amp;rsquo;s film follows a schoolteacher named Emi (Katia Pascariu) who must face the consequences of a personal sex tape being leaked on the internet. Forced to meet the school&amp;rsquo;s parents demanding her dismissal, Emi refuses to surrender, forcing an incendiary comic confrontation. &amp;nbsp;Jude as modern visionary shines through in the film where he takes the viewer on a journey through an array of different lenses; an ode to the French New Wave one moment, the next is Surrealistic and brash, creating a film that is as mesmerizing as it is uncategorizable &amp;ndash; all while delivering scathing social commentary on hypocrisy and prejudice in our societies. &amp;nbsp;WINNER &amp;ndash; GOLDEN BEAR &amp;ndash;2021 BERLIN INTERNATIONAL FILM FESTIVAL&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;MAN IN THE FIELD: THE LIFE AND ART OF JIM DENEVAN&lt;br /&gt;
