ing the filmmakers&amp;#39; mission to grow the nature-connecting movement.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;The film&amp;rsquo;s director, Sylvie Rokab, will be present for a Q&amp;amp;A. You are invited to join afterward in Forbes for refreshments and a chance to learn more about how the Green Committee and the church&amp;#39;s community partners are working on environmental and climate justice in Santa Monica/LA and beyond.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

