&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; outline:0px; font-size:12px; background:transparent&quot;&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt;Cine Sin Fronteras (Cinema without Borders). &amp;mdash;A Mini Film Festival Experience with Beverages, Music, Special Guest Q&amp;amp;A, Presented at the Mexican Consulate of Los Angeles!!! The Latin American Cinemateca of Los Angeles (LACLA) will present 2 spectacular film shorts, &amp;ldquo;Refugio&amp;rdquo; (Refuge) &amp;amp; &amp;ldquo;La selva negra&amp;rdquo; (The Modern Jungle) on Friday 08 September 2017.&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px&quot; /&gt;
&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; outline:0px; font-size:12px; background:transparent&quot;&gt;Refugio (Refuge)&lt;/strong&gt;Co-directed by Eloi Chavez and Mayra Caal Gaspar.&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px&quot; /&gt;
Through the eyes of Mayra, we learn about the lives in Mexico of Amalia and Roberto, two former refugees who fled on foot from Guatemala, and the process they have had to go through in order to reconstruct themselves, regardless of the trauma of the genocide perpetrated by the army warfare. In Spanish only.&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px&quot; /&gt;
&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; outline:0px; font-size:12px; background:transparent&quot;&gt;La selva negra (The Modern Jungle)&lt;/strong&gt;Co-directed by Charles Fairbanks and Saul Kak. A portrait of globalization filtered through the fever dream of a Zoque shaman, Juan, who falls under the spell of a pyramid scheme marketed nutritional supplement. Nearby, Carmen lives peacefully off the land her martyred husband paid for with his life. The Modern Jungle documents their encounters with modernity&amp;mdash;including capitalism, commodity fetish, and cinema itself. Screened last year at Slamdance. Spanish, subtitled in English.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

