&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; outline:0px; font-size:12px; background:transparent&quot;&gt;DESCRIPTION&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Playing Real Good, for FREE! The Highland Park Independent Film Festival is glad to be announcing their community sponsorship for this year&amp;#39;s &amp;quot;Play Music On The Porch Day&amp;quot; on August 26th. They will be screening the best videos from around the World at the Highland Park Senior Center from 6-830pm. This event is FREE and for more information contact Monica at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:monica@playmusicontheporchday.com&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; outline:none; font-size:12px; background:transparent; text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;monica@playmusicontheporchday.com&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp; Sat, August 26, 2017, Play Music on the Porch Day, is an international day of music. In just 4 years it has grown from a few musicians playing in Highland Park, California to an international event. In 2016 thousands of musicians from at least 17 countries participated, including Mongolia, Algeria and Iran. 2017 promises to be even bigger! Join in and play along with musicians from around the world on the last Saturday in August to celebrate Play Music on the Porch Day. Participation is easy! Just go outside and play music Participate alone or invite your friends to gather on the porch, in the yard or down on the corner out in the street. Share a video on your favorite social media platform and use&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/playmusicontheporchday&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; outline:none; font-size:12px; background:transparent; text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;#playmusicontheporchday&lt;/a&gt;. Also, DON&amp;#39;T FORGET!!! August 8th is the LATE SUBMISSION DEADLINE for this year&amp;#39;s Highland Park Independent Film Festival!!! Wrap &amp;#39;em put, put &amp;#39;em in the can, and send them over to the HPIFF