&lt;strong style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; outline:0px; font-size:12px; background:transparent&quot;&gt;DESCRIPTION:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Marvel Studios&amp;rsquo; GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY 2 is funny, full of heart, and a visual feast, reprising the roles of a most unconventional cast of Marvel comic book heroes: Star-Lord--The half-human leader of the Guardians , Gamora--an orphan seeking redemption for past crimes, Drax the Destroyer--a muscled warrior in search for vengeance, Baby Groot--a tree-like humanoid and sidekick of&amp;hellip;Rocket&amp;mdash;a&amp;nbsp; raccoon mercenary, master of weapons and battle tactics! The Guardians travel throughout the cosmos and struggle to keep their new-found family together, while helping Star Lord learn more about his true parentage and stopping a enemy who threatens to destroy the entire galaxy. Sounds like FUN?&amp;nbsp; It is, and you can call&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;tel:(818)%20985-2711&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px; padding:0px; border:0px; outline:none; font-size:12px; background:transparent; text-decoration:none&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; value=&quot;+18189852711&quot;&gt;818-985-2711&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for available tickets to a special advanced screening on May 1st at the AMC Burbank 16 if you&amp;rsquo;re a Film Clubber. It&amp;rsquo;s the same number to resubscribe or join the Film Club.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

