e-height:17.12px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:0px; font-size:16px; margin:0px; padding:0px; border-radius:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;outline:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif&quot;&gt;. &amp;nbsp;This triptych of horror tales is presided over with assurance and some seriously mordant wit by Jeremy Dyson and Andy Nyman.&amp;rdquo; &amp;ndash; Philip De Semlyen, Time Out&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing:inherit&quot; /&gt;
