:0px; font-size:16px; margin:0px; padding:0px; border-radius:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;outline:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif&quot;&gt;Description:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:0px; font-size:12pt; margin:0px; padding:0px; border-radius:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;outline:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:0px; font-size:16px; margin:0px; padding:0px; border-radius:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;outline:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;LOU ANDREAS-SALOM&amp;Eacute;, THE AUDACITY TO BE FREE, An Amazing Biopic at the Most Fabulous Laemmle Royal!!!&amp;nbsp; Lou Andreas-Salom&amp;eacute;, the woman who enraptured 19th century Europe&amp;#39;s greatest minds, recounts her life to Ernst Pfeiffer in this German film directed by Cordula Post-Kablutz. &amp;nbsp;A published novelist, poet and essayist, Salom&amp;eacute;&amp;#39;s desire to live a life free from convention scandalized society but spurred genius and passion in others, including Friedrich Nietzsche, Paul R&amp;eacute;e and her lover, the poet Rainer Marie Rilke. &amp;nbsp;Under the tutelage of Sigmund Freud, she became the first female psychoanalyst.&amp;nbsp; QUOTES: &amp;ldquo;Kablitz-Post&amp;rsquo;s feature film debut is marvelous at unraveling the tangle of relationships surrounding this rebellious figure.&amp;rdquo; - Katja Iken, Der Spiegel Online;&amp;nbsp; &amp;quot;With intelligence and sensitivity, [the film traces] the extraordinary life of a brave woman who defied her time and insisted on her freedom.&amp;rdquo; - Thierry Gandillot, Les Echos, France;&amp;nbsp; &amp;ldquo;What the film evokes ultimately is that you can be a feminist, an intellectual, a writer, even a hard-to-get player, and still maintain around you an array of men who would do anything&amp;mdash;bring her flowers, cut their wrists, divorce their wives, write over-the-top poetry&amp;mdash;just to revel in the aura she exudes.&amp;rdquo;- Harvey Karten, New York Film Critics Online.&amp;nbsp; AWARDS: Grand Prize Narrative Feature &amp;ndash; Socially Relevnt Film Festival NYC; NDR Newcomer Award (Audience Award) Internationales Filmfest Emden-Norderney Emden, Germany (Juni, 2016); Golden Bretzel Award German Film Week of Dinard &amp;nbsp;Dinard, France (Mai, 2017, 5th edition&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

