&lt;b style=&quot;box-sizing:inherit; font-weight:bold&quot;&gt;Description&lt;/b&gt;: One of the Late 20th Century&amp;rsquo;s Most Intriguing and Iconic Artists in New Documentary&amp;mdash; GRACE JONES: BLOODLIGHT AND BAMI. &amp;nbsp;Director Sophie Fiennes presents a new up-close-and-personal look at Grace Jones. This electrifying journey through the public and private worlds of pop culture mega-icon Grace Jones contrasts musical sequences with intimate personal footage, all the while brimming with Jones&amp;rsquo;s bold aesthetic. A larger-than-life entertainer, an androgynous glam-pop diva, an unpredictable media presence &amp;ndash; Grace Jones excelled all being these things, and more. Fiennes&amp;rsquo;s documentary goes beyond the traditional music biography, offering a portrait as stylish and unconventional as its subject. &amp;ldquo;&lt;span style=&quot;border:0px; font-size:16px; margin:0px; padding:0px; border-radius:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;outline:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:inherit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;, sans-serif&quot;&gt;★★★★★&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. &amp;nbsp;Shot over five years, Sophie Fiennes&amp;rsquo; fly-on-the-wall documentary of the pop-culture icon-cum-provocateur Grace Jones is a fascinating look at the life of a true original.&amp;rdquo; &amp;ndash; James Croot, StuffNZ; &amp;nbsp;&amp;ldquo;Bloodlight and Bami presents Grace Jones as she is: beautiful and strong, sensitive and fierce.&amp;rdquo; &amp;ndash; Tom Duggins, CineVue; &amp;ldquo;Rarely has a combination of filmmaker and subject been so thrillingly perfect.&amp;rdquo; &amp;ndash; Elena Lazic, Seventh Row;&amp;nbsp; &amp;ldquo;Bloodlight And Bami has the stuff to be an instant cult classic.&amp;rdquo; &amp;ndash; Kevin Ritchie, NOW Toronto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&l