&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Donate your used vehicle and show your support for KPFK!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://kpfk.careasy.org/home&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://mm.aiircdn.com/427/5bd8bcc181c9d.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float: right; margin-left: 5px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) 0px 2px 10px; border-radius: 4px; width: 352.969px; height: 184.931px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Interested in donating your car or van or truck for the benefit of KPFK?&amp;nbsp;It&amp;#39;s easy to make a contribution that supports KPFK!&amp;nbsp;YOU&amp;nbsp;CAN&amp;nbsp;NOW&amp;nbsp;DONATE&amp;nbsp;YOUR&amp;nbsp;VEHICLE&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;402525421-05012007&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;TO KPFK&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;ONLINE&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
Here&amp;#39;s how it works:&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
Just call Toll-Free 877-KPFK-AUTO or 877-573-5288 to speak to our&amp;nbsp;KPFK Vehicle Donation Representative or email&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:donations@charitableautoresources.com&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;donations@charitableautoresources.com&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;You can donate your vehicle to KPFK online [&lt;a href=&quot;https://kpfk.careasy.org/home&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; text-decoration: none;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;here&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; list-style-position: inside; list-style-type: square; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li class=&quot;firstItem&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(30, 116, 156);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Our Representative will schedule a pickup that&amp;#39;s convenient for you, and provide you with confirmation of your donation. If you donate your car after January 1, 2006, we will mail you a confirmation that states how much money your vehicle sold for at auction. This amount is what you actually claim on the itemized tax return. According to the tax law effective January 1, 2005, if the claimed value of the donated vehicle exceeds $500, the taxpayer is limited to the gross proceeds of the sale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;General Questions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;What are the benefits of donating my car to KPFK 90.7FM?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
KPFK 90.7FM benefits by receiving a cash donation to fund new and existing programs and increase community awareness through local events.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;You benefit by being able to reduce your taxable income when taxes are itemized. Plus you avoid the costs associated with selling your car. No need to pay for advertising, no loss of privacy and possible security risk, and no need to pay for vehicle registration, insurance, and repairs to keep your car in running condition while you wait for a buyer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;Does my car have to be running to donate it?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
In some cases we can take your car, running or not. However, it must have an engine and be tow-able. Contact a representative at 877-KPFK-AUTO or 877-573-5288 to find out if your vehicle qualifies for pick-up.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;Do you only accept cars for donation?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
Many types of motor vehicles are accepted including boats, motorcycles, trucks, and cars. If you are uncertain as to whether or not your vehicle is eligible, please contact the vehicle donation program toll free at 877-KPFK-AUTO or 877-573-5288&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;How long will it take to pick up my vehicle?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
We make donating your car as simple and convenient as possible. In many cases, vehicles can be picked up the same day. Call our representatives at 877-KPFK-AUTO or 877-573-5288&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;Do I have to be with the vehicle at the time of pick-up?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
No. Special arrangements can be made by calling our representative.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;What paperwork do I need?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
The only paperwork needed is a signed, clear title (pink slip). Have your title with you when you call-in your donation. [Please note: a clear title indicates the title is in the name of the donor without a lien].&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;Do I need a smog certificate in order to donate my car?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
For states that require smog certificates or safety inspections, you may donate your vehicle without these documents.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;What if I receive legal notices?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
In the rare event that you receive any notification of a lien sale, DMV actions or other activity related to your donated vehicle, please contact us at 877-KPFK-AUTO or 877-573-5288 immediately for assistance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;Tax Questions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;How does the new law effect my tax deduction?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
Donors are no longer responsible for determining the deductible value of their donation. Instead, they will receive IRS Form 1098-C, Contributions of Motor Vehicles, Boats, and Airplanes if the proceeds from the sale exceed $500, stating the amount of the gross proceeds from the sale of the donated vehicle. The amount listed on IRS Form 1098-C, Contributions of Motor Vehicles, Boats, and Airplanes will be the gross proceeds of the deductible donation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;Will I get a tax receipt for my donation?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
Yes, our driver will issue a receipt at the time of pick-up. This is not your final tax receipt unless the sale of your vehicle does not exceed $500. This initial acknowledgement will indicate your name as well as the year, make, model and condition of the car you are donating. It will be your only receipt if your vehicle sells for less than $500.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;An IRS Form 1098-C, Contributions of Motor Vehicles, Boats, and Airplanes will be mailed to you within 30 days of the sale stating the amount of gross proceeds received from your car, provided your vehicle sold for more than $500. This will be your tax receipt for your charitable contribution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;How is the value determined on the vehicle donated?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
The value is determined by the gross proceeds raised from the sale of the donated vehicle. You no longer have the burden of determining the value yourself.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;Does the new law affect KPFK 90.7FM?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
KPFK 90.7FM has additional paperwork in reporting the gross proceeds raised from the sale of the vehicle to the donor and IRS. The process of obtaining the cash donation from the vehicle remains the same.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;What can I claim as a deduction?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
According to the tax law effective January 1, 2005, if the claimed value of the donated vehicle exceeds $500, the taxpayer is limited to the gross proceeds of the sale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; background: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent; font-family: &amp;quot;lucida sans unicode&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;lucida grande&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; background: transparent;&quot;&gt;What if my car is valued over $5000?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot; /&gt;
Effective January 1, 2005, you are no longer required to have vehicles appraised. The value you may claim will be the amount of gross proceeds received from your vehicle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KPFK&amp;#39;s Community Partners&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KPFK&lt;/strong&gt; is now accepting underwriting from local small businesses, community organizations, cooperatives, and other non-profit organizations that are in alignment with our mission and with the values of our diverse Southern California audience and listeners. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;If you have suggestions for enterprises and organizations that might help underwrite KPFK in return for an on-air announcement of their support, as well as a listing in our Dispatch and here on the website, please send along information about the prospect, along with whom to contact, to comments [at] kpfk.org.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;Currently support for KPFK comes from:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UCLA&amp;#39;s Center for the Art of Performance&lt;/strong&gt; - more information about their offerings at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://cap.ucla.edu/&quot;&gt;https://cap.ucla.edu/&lt;/a&gt;; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;and from:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Elderosa Elderberry Ranch&lt;/strong&gt;, makers of elderberry gummies from fresh-picked wild elderberries on their ranch and elderflower honey from their hives. More information at &lt;a href=&quot;https://elderosaelderberry.com&quot;&gt;https://elderosaelderberry.com&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;We appreciate their support for the station and look forward to building many such ongoing relationships that benefit you, our listeners, and help the station continue to serve the community and improve out program offerings. A full and growing list of our community partners will be available here.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;You can learn more about the program on the home page of kpfk.org, or click &lt;a href=&quot;/community-underwriting-intake-form/&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; to initiate the process of becoming an underwriter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;aiircomponent id=&quot;110&quot; type=&quot;form&quot;&gt;
&lt;/aiircomponent&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you would like to pledge support for the station, either as a one-time donation (with or without a request for a thank you gift) or for a sustainer pledge monthly, but don&amp;#39;t have a credit card or perhaps not even a bank account, fill out this form to let us know your basic information, the amount you&amp;#39;d like to donate and the frequency, and what thank-you gift, if any that you would like. We will send you an invoice or bill that you can pay with a money order or check.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1&gt;KPFK&amp;nbsp;Media Sponsorship Requests&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;KPFK partners with non-profit organizations seeking radio promotion of their events in exchange for promotion of Pacifica Radio KPFK 90.7 to organization&amp;rsquo;s constituents, affiliates and friends through printed, web and other marketing tools utilized by the requesting organization. To request media sponsorship from KPFK, please fill out the attached document for your event and send it back with the promotional pieces you&amp;rsquo;re using to promote your event (press release, flyer, etc.). We will also ask you to prepare a web banner for use on our KPFK website, and promotional radio copy for the radio spot. Specifications follow.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;KPFK Media Sponsorship&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
We usually offer a 14-day on-air and online Event Calendar promotion. Promos are generally scheduled 2-3 times per day. Home page web promotion within the &amp;ldquo;Featured Events&amp;rdquo; section is&amp;nbsp; 1 week prior to the opening of your event.&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;The precise details of your promotion will be confirmed upon the return of your&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://pacifica.org/kpfkreq/olor_form.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;MEDIA SPONSORSHIP REQUEST FORM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
As a trade, KPFK requests that the station be promoted to your constituents, via print, web and any other available means of promotion, e.g. the placement of our logo on the event website as a Media Sponsor; and that a certain number of tickets or passes be made available to our listeners as a giveaway. (Our KPFK logos pack will be sent to you upon approval of the Media Sponsorship.)&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Specs for on-air promo spot:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
1. No calls to action.&lt;br /&gt;
2. No mention of prices (even the word &amp;quot;free&amp;quot;).&lt;br /&gt;
3. No mention of commercial or corporate sponsors.&lt;br /&gt;
4. Promo should be written in the style of an announcement.&lt;br /&gt;
5. Direct audience to the KPFK website for further information. (KPFK links to the organizer&amp;rsquo;s website and/or Facebook Event page.) Include your event&amp;rsquo;s contact phone number.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Specs for web banner:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Jpeg or PNG, 72 dpi, 400 pixels high x 840 pixels wide (horizontal layout).&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
If you have any questions, call (818) 985-2711 ext. 326.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://pacifica.org/kpfkreq/olor_form.php&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;MEDIA SPONSORSHIP REQUEST FORM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

