&lt;aiirhtmlblock title=&quot;Pitch a show?&quot;&gt;&lt;!-- PITCH A SHOW PAGE - KPFK --&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;color:#111; font-family:sans-serif; padding:.5rem 1rem;&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div style=&quot;max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;font-size:1.1rem; line-height:1.6; text-align:center; margin-bottom:2rem;&quot;&gt;Got something to say that commercial media won’t touch? We’re always looking for bold, local voices with ideas that inform, challenge, or move people. If you’ve got a show idea—news, music, storytelling, roundtable, bilingual, experimental—let’s talk.&lt;/p&gt;

    &lt;div style=&quot;background:#ffffff; border:1px solid #ddd; padding:1.5rem; margin-bottom:2rem; border-radius:6px;&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2 style=&quot;font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;&quot;&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/h2&gt;

      &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size:1.05rem; line-height:1.8; padding-left:1.25rem; list-style:disc;&quot;&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Original ideas rooted in justice, culture, or community&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Local relevance or underserved perspectives&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Clear point of view (but not just punditry)&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Passion over polish—experience helps, but it’s not required&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;div style=&quot;background:#ffffff; border:1px solid #ddd; padding:1.5rem; border-radius:6px;&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2 style=&quot;font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;&quot;&gt;How to Pitch&lt;/h2&gt;

      &lt;p style=&quot;font-size:1.05rem; line-height:1.6;&quot;&gt;Send us 1–2 paragraphs about your idea, the audience it serves, and what makes it different. If you have a demo (audio or video), include a link—but it’s not required.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;!-- Embedded Google Form --&gt;

    &lt;div style=&quot;margin-top:3rem;&quot;&gt;
      &lt;iframe frameborder=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;997&quot; marginheight=&quot;0&quot; marginwidth=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScychLVeM8D8UsjkZUjYaFM3HGXZ82stSqwHC5OuZy8d5llpw/viewform?embedded=true&quot; style=&quot;border:none;&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;&gt;Loading…&lt;/iframe&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/aiirhtmlblock&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://kpfk.wedid.it/campaigns/8909-spring-drive-2021&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;PLEASE CLICK THIS LINK TO ACCES OUR NEW &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

